Sentencas: The application of an inkjet printing process for fabricating solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) cathodes was investigated.
Titulo: Application of a thin intermediate cathode layer prepared by inkjet printing for SOFCs

Sentencas: Stably-dispersed LSCF-GDC inks were prepared by ball milling, and the composition was easily controlled by the preparation process.
Titulo: Application of a thin intermediate cathode layer prepared by inkjet printing for SOFCs

Sentencas: Fabrication of an LSCF-GDC layer was successfully carried out by depositing dots and the thickness was easily controlled by repeating printing process.
Titulo: Application of a thin intermediate cathode layer prepared by inkjet printing for SOFCs

Sentencas: A planar SOFC single cell with a double-layered cathode (comprised of a paste painted cathode layer and an inkjet printed interlayer) achieved a maximum power density of 0.71 W/cm(2) at 600 degrees C.
Titulo: Application of a thin intermediate cathode layer prepared by inkjet printing for SOFCs

Sentencas: This is the preliminary work for fabricating the cathode layer of a SOFC single cell via inkjet printing.
Titulo: Application of a thin intermediate cathode layer prepared by inkjet printing for SOFCs
